form_title: Application for Withdrawal from General Provident Fund

fields.question_template: What is the name of the subscriber?
fields.description: Full name of the GPF account subscriber
fields.purpose: To identify the GPF account holder

fields.question_template: What is your designation?
fields.description: Job title or designation of the subscriber
fields.purpose: To identify the official position of the subscriber

fields.question_template: What is your GPF Account Number with Departmental Suffix?
fields.description: GPF account number including departmental suffix
fields.purpose: To identify the specific GPF account

fields.question_template: What is your current pay?
fields.description: Current salary/pay of the subscriber
fields.purpose: To record the subscriber's current pay

fields.question_template: What is your date of joining service?
fields.description: Date when the subscriber joined service
fields.purpose: To record the service commencement date

fields.question_template: What is your date of superannuation?
fields.description: Expected retirement/superannuation date
fields.purpose: To record the expected retirement date

fields.question_template: For which year is the A/C Statement?
fields.description: Year of the account statement
fields.purpose: To identify the financial year of statement

fields.semantic_label: Closing balance as per A/C Statement (Rs.)
fields.question_template: What is the closing balance as per A/C Statement?
fields.description: Closing balance amount in rupees
fields.purpose: To record the closing balance from account statement

fields.question_template: From what date is the credit for monthly subscription?
fields.description: Start date for monthly subscription credit
fields.purpose: To record subscription credit period start

fields.question_template: To what date is the credit for monthly subscription?
fields.description: End date for monthly subscription credit
fields.purpose: To record subscription credit period end

fields.question_template: What is the monthly subscription amount?
fields.description: Amount credited on account of monthly subscription
fields.purpose: To record monthly subscription credit amount

fields.semantic_label: Refunds made to the fund after closing balance (Rs.)
fields.question_template: What is the amount of refunds made to the fund after closing balance?
fields.description: Refunds made to fund after closing balance vide (i) above
fields.purpose: To record any refunds made to the fund

fields.question_template: From what date was the withdrawal period?
fields.description: Start date of withdrawal period
fields.purpose: To record withdrawal period start date

fields.question_template: To what date was the withdrawal period?
fields.description: End date of withdrawal period
fields.purpose: To record withdrawal period end date

fields.question_template: What is the withdrawal amount during the period?
fields.description: Amount withdrawn during the specified period
fields.purpose: To record withdrawal amount

fields.semantic_label: Net balance at credit on the date of application (Rs.)
fields.question_template: What is the net balance at credit on the date of application?
fields.description: Net balance available as of application date
fields.purpose: To calculate available balance for withdrawal

fields.question_template: What is the amount of withdrawal required?
fields.description: Amount the subscriber wishes to withdraw
fields.purpose: To record requested withdrawal amount

fields.semantic_label: Purpose for which the withdrawal is required
fields.question_template: What is the purpose for which the withdrawal is required?
fields.description: Reason for requesting the withdrawal
fields.purpose: To justify the withdrawal request

fields.semantic_label: Rule under which the Request is covered
fields.question_template: Under which rule is the withdrawal request covered?
fields.description: Applicable GPF rule for the withdrawal
fields.purpose: To identify the applicable rule for withdrawal

fields.semantic_label: Whether any withdrawal was taken for the same purpose earlier
fields.question_template: Whether any withdrawal was taken for the same purpose earlier? If so, indicate the amount and the year.
fields.description: Details of any previous withdrawal for same purpose including amount and year
fields.purpose: To track previous withdrawals for same purpose

fields.semantic_label: Name of the Account Officer Maintaining the Provident Fund Account
fields.question_template: What is the name of the Account Officer maintaining the Provident Fund Account?
fields.description: Name of officer responsible for maintaining the GPF account
fields.purpose: To identify the responsible account officer

fields.question_template: What is the date of application?
fields.description: Date when the application is submitted
fields.purpose: To record the application submission date

fields.question_template: Please provide your signature.
fields.description: Signature of the applicant
fields.purpose: To authenticate the application

fields.question_template: What is your name?
fields.description: Name of the applicant below signature
fields.purpose: To confirm identity of signatory

fields.question_template: What is your designation?
fields.description: Designation of the applicant below signature
fields.purpose: To confirm position of signatory

fields.question_template: What is your section?
fields.description: Section/department of the applicant
fields.purpose: To identify the applicant's section
